 xlink:href="12859_2022_4943_Article_Equ2.gif" position="anchor"/></alternatives></disp-formula>Non-canonical base pairs do not contribute to the energy in the model.</p>
    <p id="Par10">For a given RNA <italic>w</italic>, a <bold>mutation</bold> is a pair <inline-formula id="IEq4"><alternatives><tex-math id="M9">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
