    <sec id="Sec10">
      <title>Interactive features</title>
      <p id="Par60">A user may further investigate a given mutation, by pressing on some row in the table to see more information about a specific mutation. For example, selecting the mutation <inline-formula id="IEq72"><alternatives><tex-math id="M151">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
