    </sec>
    <sec id="Sec11">
      <title>Analysis of mutations sets for random sequences</title>
      <p id="Par61">The importance of considering indels in the prediction of deleterious sets of mutations is illustrated by Fig. <xref rid="Fig3" ref-type="fig">3</xref> and Fig. <xref rid="Fig4" ref-type="fig">4</xref>. In this analysis, 100 sets of <inline-formula id="IEq73"><alternatives><tex-math id="M153">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
