				\begin{document}$$M=5$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M154"><mml:mrow><mml:mi>M</mml:mi><mml:mo>=</mml:mo><mml:mn>5</mml:mn></mml:mrow></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12859_2022_4943_Article_IEq73.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> deleterious mutations were predicted for 10 random sequences of length 200 nts, respectively, in the presence and absence of support for indels.<fig id="Fig3"><label>Fig. 3</label><caption><p>Distributions of base-pair distance to the WT MFE of mutations sets (<inline-formula id="IEq74"><alternatives><tex-math id="M155">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
